data.description: Seller has a 3.625% Assumable  roughly $645,000 mortgage. New Lanai Feb 2024 Boasting unobstructed direct  sailboat access to the Gulf of Mexico via the world-famous Matlacha Pass. This modern home offers three spacious bedrooms, three bathrooms, and a den which is currently a home office. A stunning kitchen is the heart of this home and features a Extra large center island, ample all-wood cabinetry, a stainless appliance suite, and a large dry pantry. Light neutral interior paint tones and beautiful wood-like tile flooring throughout highlight this home's contemporary design. A large shaded under-truss lanai has kevlar hurricane panels that allows the entire area to be shade and sheltered, With a push of a remote the kevlar opens to a beautiful, sun deck with  heated pool and spa finished with a paver deck making it the perfect spot to relax and watch the Florida sunsets. Fully automated pool equipment that can be controlled from a phone or tablet from anywhere with internet . Additional features include a three-car garage, impact glass windows and doors. Ideal for a family, perfect for a getaway and a captain's dream. Housing is be sold furnished with a few personal exclusions.
